Key needs and features:
  add items in different category 
  stock update when items are added, removed or sold.
  item price update, including discount
  product rating feature
  create customer account
  item selection and collection (add to cart, including save for later retrieval)
  Online ordering and delivery 
        - Secure payment system
        - End to end delivery system, including tracking 
        - product return and refund 
        
List of Stakeholders 
        - Consumers (could be individual, organizations, other big companies)
        - Suppliers, those companies which would like to sell their product on the e-shop platform 
        - Courier/logistic service providers (for product delivery and product loading) 
        - Other e-shop service providers, which would like to work in collaboration with (this is  optional but there could be scenarios that it may work well)

